description._content: Title: [H. P. Dyer, Bonham, Texas] Creator: Woolley, S. P. Date: 1855 Part Of: Lawrence T. Jones III Texas photography collection Place: Texas Description: S. P. Woolley (or S. J. Wooley ?) was an early Texas travelling photographer active in Marshall, Bonham and Clarksville, Texas from the late 1850s - 1860s. Physical Description: 1 photograph: sixth plate daguerreotype; 8.3 x 7 cm.
